com.alvermont.terraj.fracplanet.util
Class TreeMapMulti

java.lang.Object
  com.alvermont.terraj.fracplanet.util.TreeMapMulti

public class TreeMapMulti
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents a data structure from the original code, a map that can hold multiple copies of the same value. We hold a TreeMap which manages a list of items for each key.
